{"article_id":"ol4rNcESPl8thQI3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"U.S. drone strikes have killed four Americans ,","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"including one","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"who was \" specifically targeted \"","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"and three others","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"who were not targets ,","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"Attorney General Eric H. Holder Jr. said in a letter to Congress on Wednesday ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"publicly confirming the strikes for the first time .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"The revelation was made a day before President Obama lays out a drone policy in a major speech at the National Defense University ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"where he also is expected to reignite his push","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to transfer detainees from the detention facility at Guantanamo Bay , Cuba ,","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"which houses suspected terrorists .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"\" He will discuss why the use of drone strikes is necessary , legal and just ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"while addressing the various issues","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"raised by our use of targeted action , \"","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"a White House official said Wednesday night ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"previewing the remarks on the condition of anonymity .","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"The official also said","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Mr. Obama has signed guidance","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"laying out the full standards for lethal strikes ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and Mr. Holder said in his letter","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that classified guidance will be provided to some members of Congress .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"After news reports last year revealed the extent of the drone strike program ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. Obama promised to seek firmer legal footing for the program","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"by going to Congress with more details ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and Wednesday ' s letter was the first step in that .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"In the five-page letter , Mr. Holder said","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"the U.S. specifically targeted Anwar al-Awlaki in a September 2011 drone strike in Yemen .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"He also listed the three other Americans","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"who","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"had been incidentally killed in strikes :","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Samir Khan , Jude Kenan Mohammed and Abderrahman Anwar al-Awlaki , the targeted man ' s son .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Mr. Holder called it \" an unfortunate but undeniable fact \"","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"that Americans had been killed ,","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"but said","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"U.S. citizenship doesn ' t make someone immune from being targeted .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"The drone executive program has been controversial","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"since it began under President George W. Bush .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Mr. Obama expanded the program ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"but use of the strikes has begun to decline .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"The New York Times reported this year","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that strikes in Pakistan peaked in 2010 ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and strikes in Yemen this year are half the rate","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"they were last year .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Still , members of Congress have demanded answers on the program ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"and Mr. Obama is preparing to give them details","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"of how he decides","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"who is placed on the targeted killing list .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"The administration will send Congress a classified document","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"laying out details","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"this week ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"and Mr. Obama will provide some public details Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"In his letter Wednesday , Mr. Holder said","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"the conditions","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"for ending up on the target list","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"are that the executive branch has determined","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"\" after a thorough and careful review \"","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"that the target poses \" an imminent threat of violent attack \" against the U.S. ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that the person can not be captured ,","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"and that the operation falls under acceptable war practices .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"al-Awlaki was put on the list","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"because he encouraged and helped the Christmas Day bomber in 2009","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"and played a key role in an October 2010 plot","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"to detonate explosives on two U.S.-bound cargo planes ,","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"including developing and testing the explosive devices .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"\" The decision","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to target Anwar al-Awlaki","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"was lawful ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"it was considered ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and it was just , \"","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"the attorney general said ,","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"that he , other Justice Department attorneys and \" other departments and agencies \" concluded","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"that al-Awlaki was an appropriate target .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Mr. Holder said","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"the administration gave \" the relevant congressional committees \" a heads-up","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"that al-Awlaki was on the kill list in February 2010 , more than a year before the fatal strike .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"One of the other men","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"killed ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Mohammed , was indicted on charges of conspiracy","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"to support terrorists","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and conspiracy","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"to commit murder in a foreign country .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Mohammed grew up in North Carolina ,","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"where he reportedly trained for the attacks","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"before going to Pakistan .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"WRAL , a television station in North Carolina , reported","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"that family members had heard","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"he was killed in a drone attack ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"but the government had not confirmed those reports .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Khan was killed in the same strike","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"that killed al-Awlaki in Yemen ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"while al-Awlaki ' s son was killed weeks later in another strike ,","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"according to reports .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Human rights groups have called on Mr. Obama to renounce drone executions as a tool in the war on terrorism ,","depth":3},{"id":96,"text":"and on Wednesday the American Civil Liberties Union said","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"the program should be subject to review in the courts .","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"\" This is a small step towards transparency ,","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"and we welcome the government ' s recognition","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"that it must publicly explain its actions","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"when it decides to kill an American citizen , \"","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"said Hina Shamsi , director of the ACLU National Security Project .","depth":6},{"id":103,"text":"\" Much more openness is still needed .","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"The government must disclose its still-secret targeted killing memos","depth":7},{"id":105,"text":"so the public can determine","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"if they contain criteria as vague and elastic as its definitions of ' imminence ' and ' feasibility of capture . ' \"","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"White House officials said","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"Mr. Obama also will use Thursday ' s speech","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"to renew his call","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"for closing the Guantanamo Bay detention facility","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"and will focus on powers","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"the administration already has","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"to transfer detainees to other countries .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"\" It is the president ' s view that we should be determined ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"as he is ,","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"to see the Guantanamo Bay detention facility closed , \"","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"White House press secretary Jay Carney said Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"\" Keeping it open is not efficient ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"it ' s not effective ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and it ' s not in the interests of our national security . \"","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Federal law blocks Mr. Obama from bringing any of the detainees at Guantanamo to the U.S. ,","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"but it does allow him to transfer them to other countries","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"- as long as the Defense Department certifies","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"that they are not likely to return to the battlefield .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"That is proved to be a difficult bar ,","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"and transfers from the prison essentially have halted .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"The prison currently holds 166 detainees ,","depth":5},{"id":128,"text":"according to The New York Times .","depth":5},{"id":129,"text":"Some of Mr. Obama ' s key Democratic allies on Capitol Hill have signaled","depth":5},{"id":130,"text":"that they would back a renewed push","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"to close Guantanamo .","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"\" Until it is closed ,","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"it will remain a symbol of attempts","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"to avoid the rule of law , \"","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"Rep. Adam Smith of Washington , the ranking Democrat on the House Armed Services Committee , said in an op-ed on the Huffington Post .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":230,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":187,"right":229,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":171,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":160,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":156,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":142,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":141,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":140,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":0,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":137,"right":138,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":137,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":145,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":7,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":8,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":149,"right":153,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":11,"right":146,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":146,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":16,"right":152,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":152,"left":150,"right":